name: a quiet afternoon
description: A quiet afternoon drowned in pastel light. This was taken after a three-year hiatus from film photography. I experimented with the different settings on my camera. Love the results. This is my favorite shot from the roll. When ordered, you will receive a 5 x 7" print of a quiet afternoon printed on Kodak Professional Endura paper with a lustre finish. The print comes in a reusable glassine bag & ships in a sturdy cardboard mailer.
